{"id": 1863, "genre": 1000, "title": "现在，当你说“朋克”的时候你在说什么？", "description": "“可以，这很朋克”里的“朋克”到底是个啥？来，唠唠。", "record_count": 5439, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170821174749RBvLsh8woUz590JV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-22T17:00:05Z", "questions": [{"id": 2828, "title": "现在，当你说“朋克”的时候你在说什么？", "content": "当你说“朋克”的时候你在说什么？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 230720, "content": "我是朋克原教旨主义者，我说的朋克就是朋克音乐", "image": "img/option/option/20170821181042LhACrQJsIFd2jzRO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230721, "content": "某种特定的外形特征表达的人生态度，例如烫头染发不爱洗头", "image": "img/option/option/20170821181438Kcg3Zv87ueJiIqCk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230722, "content": "抽烟/喝酒/熬夜表达自己的人生态度，一种折腾自己个儿的生活习惯", "image": "img/option/option/20170821181338GLPhB9pkjF15tinQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230723, "content": "一种以马丁靴，皮夹克、破洞裤子为代表的时尚风格背后的人生态度", "image": "img/option/option/20170821181350TQhZv4uV8xHPAN7e.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230724, "content": "一种不合作、爱咋咋地的气质，不想去同学聚会的奶奶“就跟他们说我死了”", "image": "img/option/option/20170821221510RbfwIS9DdcxvYCWo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230725, "content": "一种消解“意义”“价值”的解构精神，比如自我调侃“上豆瓣，做无价值用户”", "image": "img/option/option/20170821222233wNtTCnO34FSdyfeG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230726, "content": "一种耿直而实在的性格，朋克系的士司机，拒载理由“我不想去”", "image": "img/option/option/20170821221451so8pnC3JbLcaAXNz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230728, "content": "一种艺术风格，“机械迷城，典型蒸汽朋克游戏”", "image": "img/option/option/20170821222141AW7eVU1HkJIlbZY2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}